Commands to type after a cvs checkout (in this order)

cd scs_lib;
aclocal
autoheader
autoconf
automake --add-missing
cd ..
aclocal
autoheader
autoconf
automake --add-missing
./configure 

or, if you want to perform accuracy tests
./configure --enable-mpfr -enable-ultim --with-gmp=/usr/local
(replace /usr/local/ with the actual location of the mpfr source)

Remark: on debian woody, use autoconf2.50


